                0.155,
                0.183,
                0.17
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 \\(\\mathrm{e}^6\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.177,
                0.514,
                0.208
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 0}(1 + 3x)^{\\frac{2}{\\sin x}} = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\left[(1 + 3x)^{\\frac{1}{3x}}\\right]^{\\frac{6x}{\\sin x}} = \\mathrm{e}^{6}.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.051,
                0.212,
                0.383,
                0.241
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 \\(-\\int_{0}^{x^{2}}\\cos t^{2}\\mathrm{d}t - 2x^{2}\\cos x^{4}.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.25,
                0.72,
                0.282
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\frac{\\mathrm{d}}{\\mathrm{d}x}\\int_{x^2}^{0}x\\cos t^2\\mathrm{d}t = -\\frac{\\mathrm{d}}{\\mathrm{d}x}\\left(x\\int_0^{x^2}\\cos t^2\\mathrm{d}t\\right) = -\\int_0^{x^2}\\cos t^2\\mathrm{d}t - 2x^2\\cos x^4.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.051,
                0.289,
                0.176,
                0.304
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(3)【答案】 4."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.31,
                0.697,
                0.327
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\left[(a + b) \\times (b + c)\\right] \\cdot (c + a) = (a \\times b + a \\times c + b \\times c) \\cdot (c + a)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.394,
                0.334,
                0.795,
                0.347
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= (\\boldsymbol {a} \\times \\boldsymbol {b}) \\cdot \\boldsymbol {c} + (\\boldsymbol {b} \\times \\boldsymbol {c}) \\cdot \\boldsymbol {a} = 2 (\\boldsymbol {a} \\times \\boldsymbol {b}) \\cdot \\boldsymbol {c} = 4.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.051,
                0.356,
                0.192,
                0.372
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（4）【答案】 \\(\\sqrt{3}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.078,
                0.378,
                0.741,
                0.413
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由 \\(\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\left|\\frac{a_{n + 1}}{a_n}\\right| = \\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\frac{n + 1}{n}\\cdot \\left|\\frac{2^n + (-3)^n}{2^{n + 1} + (-3)^{n + 1}}\\right| = \\frac{1}{3}\\) 得收敛半径 \\(R = \\sqrt{3}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.051,
                0.419,
                0.259,
                0.474
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(5)【答案】 \\(\\begin{pmatrix} 3 & 0 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 2 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{pmatrix}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.078,
                0.482,
                0.769,
                0.52
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由 \\(A^{-1}BA = 6A + BA\\) 得 \\(BA = 6A^2 + ABA\\) ，然后右乘 \\(A^{-1}\\) 得 \\(B = 6A + AB\\) 解得 \\(B = 6(E - A)^{-1}A = 6[A^{-1}(E - A)]^{-1} = 6(A^{-1} - E)^{-1}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.527,
                0.755,
                0.631
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(\\mathbf{A}^{-1} - \\mathbf{E} = \\begin{pmatrix} 2 & 0 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 3 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 0 & 6 \\end{pmatrix}\\), 得 \\((\\mathbf{A}^{-1} - \\mathbf{E})^{-1} = \\begin{bmatrix} \\frac{1}{2} & 0 & 0 \\\\ 0 & \\frac{1}{3} & 0 \\\\ 0 & 0 & \\frac{1}{6} \\end{bmatrix}\\), 故 \\(\\mathbf{B} = \\begin{pmatrix} 3 & 0 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 2 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{pmatrix}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.051,
                0.637,
                0.138,
                0.652
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "二、选择题"
        },
        {
