                0.68,
                0.724,
                0.696
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】直线 \\(L\\) 的方向向量为 \\(\\pmb {s} = \\{1,3,2\\} \\times \\{2, - 1, - 10\\} = \\{-28,14, - 7\\}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.337,
                0.703,
                0.485,
                0.716
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= - 7 \\{4, - 2, 1 \\},\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.723,
                0.6,
                0.738
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为平面 \\(\\pi\\) 的法向量平行于 \\(L\\) 的方向向量，所以 \\(L\\perp \\pi\\) ，选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.051,
                0.744,
                0.195,
                0.759
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 (B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.078,
                0.765,
                0.663,
                0.78
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由拉格朗日中值定理得 \\(f(1) - f(0) = f'(c)\\)，其中 \\(0 < c < 1\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.785,
                0.799,
                0.802
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(f^{\\prime \\prime}(x) > 0\\) 得 \\(f^{\\prime}(x)\\) 单调递增，再由 \\(0 < c < 1\\) 得 \\(f^{\\prime}(1) > f^{\\prime}(c) > f^{\\prime}(0)\\)，应选(B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.051,
                0.807,
                0.198,
                0.822
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（3）【答案】 （A)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.829,
                0.643,
                0.861
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(F_{-}^{\\prime}(0) = \\lim_{x\\to 0^{-}}\\frac{F(x) - F(0)}{x} = \\lim_{x\\to 0^{-}}\\frac{f(x)(1 - \\sin x) - f(0)}{x}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.206,
                0.868,
                0.669,
                0.898
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0 ^ {-}} \\left[ \\frac {f (x) - f (0)}{x} - f (x) \\cdot \\frac {\\sin x}{x} \\right] = f ^ {\\prime} (0) - f (0);\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.082,
                0.904,
                0.586,
                0.935
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nF _ {+} ^ {\\prime} (0) = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0 ^ {+}} \\frac {F (x) - F (0)}{x} = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0 ^ {+}} \\frac {f (x) (1 + \\sin x) - f (0)}{x}\n\\]"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.154,
                0.071,
                0.623,
                0.102
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0 ^ {+}} \\left[ \\frac {f (x) - f (0)}{x} + f (x) \\cdot \\frac {\\sin x}{x} \\right] = f ^ {\\prime} (0) + f (0),\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.107,
                0.807,
                0.144
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(F(x)\\) 在 \\(x = 0\\) 处可导的充分必要条件是 \\(f^{\\prime}(0) - f(0) = f^{\\prime}(0) + f(0)\\)，即 \\(f(0) = 0\\)，即 \\(f(0) = 0\\) 是 \\(F(x)\\) 在 \\(x = 0\\) 处可导的充分必要条件，应选(A)."
