                0.206
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由 \\(\\left\\{\\ln \\left(1 + \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{n}}\\right)\\right\\}\\) 单调递减且 \\(\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\ln \\left(1 + \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{n}}\\right) = 0\\) 得 \\(\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}u_n\\) 收敛，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
