                0.092,
                0.213,
                0.631,
                0.248
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(u_{n}^{2} = \\ln^{2}\\left(1 + \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{n}}\\right)\\sim \\frac{1}{n}\\) 且 \\(\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}\\frac{1}{n}\\) 发散得 \\(\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}u_n^2\\) 发散，应选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.062,
                0.253,
                0.208,
