                0.29
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】将 \\(\\mathbf{A}\\) 的第1行加到第3行，再将第1行与第2行对调得 \\(\\mathbf{B}\\)，即"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.296,
                0.503,
                0.352
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(\\pmb{B} = \\left( \\begin{array}{lll}0 & 1 & 0\\\\ 1 & 0 & 0\\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{array} \\right)\\left( \\begin{array}{lll}1 & 0 & 0\\\\ 0 & 1 & 0\\\\ 1 & 0 & 1 \\end{array} \\right)\\pmb {A} = \\pmb{P}_1\\pmb{P}_2\\pmb {A}\\) ，应选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.062,
                0.359,
