            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【解】 \\(\\Sigma :z = \\sqrt{x^2 + y^2}\\) ，其中 \\(x^{2} + y^{2}\\leqslant 2x\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.347,
                0.117,
                0.67,
                0.153
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\frac {\\partial z}{\\partial x} = \\frac {x}{\\sqrt {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2}}}, \\quad \\frac {\\partial z}{\\partial y} = \\frac {y}{\\sqrt {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2}}},\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.16,
                0.896,
                0.202
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(\\iint_{\\Sigma} z \\, \\mathrm{d}S = \\iint_{x^2 + y^2 \\leqslant 2x} \\sqrt{x^2 + y^2} \\cdot \\sqrt{1 + \\frac{x^2}{x^2 + y^2} + \\frac{y^2}{x^2 + y^2}} \\, \\mathrm{d}x \\, \\mathrm{d}y = \\iint_{x^2 + y^2 \\leqslant 2x} \\sqrt{x^2 + y^2} \\cdot \\sqrt{2} \\, \\mathrm{d}x \\, \\mathrm{d}y\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.18,
                0.205,
                0.765,
                0.239
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= \\sqrt {2} \\int_ {- \\frac {\\pi}{2}} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} d \\theta \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\cos \\theta} r ^ {2} d r = \\frac {8}{3} \\sqrt {2} \\int_ {- \\frac {\\pi}{2}} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} \\cos^ {3} \\theta d \\theta = \\frac {1 6}{3} \\sqrt {2} \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} \\cos^ {3} \\theta d \\theta = \\frac {3 2}{9} \\sqrt {2}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.242,
                0.479,
