            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【解】 将 \\(f(x)\\) 进行偶延拓再进行周期延拓，则"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.265,
                0.42,
                0.294
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\na _ {0} = \\frac {2}{2} \\int_ {0} ^ {2} f (x) \\mathrm {d} x = \\int_ {0} ^ {2} (x - 1) \\mathrm {d} x = 0;\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
