            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} a _ {n} = \\frac {2}{2} \\int_ {0} ^ {2} f (x) \\cos \\frac {n \\pi x}{2} d x = \\int_ {0} ^ {2} (x - 1) \\cos \\frac {n \\pi x}{2} d x \\\\ = \\frac {2}{n \\pi} \\int_ {0} ^ {2} (x - 1) d \\left(\\sin \\frac {n \\pi x}{2}\\right) = \\frac {2}{n \\pi} (x - 1) \\sin \\frac {n \\pi x}{2} \\Bigg | _ {0} ^ {2} - \\frac {2}{n \\pi} \\int_ {0} ^ {2} \\sin \\frac {n \\pi x}{2} d x \\\\ = \\frac {4}{n ^ {2} \\pi^ {2}} \\cos \\frac {n \\pi x}{2} \\Big | _ {0} ^ {2} = \\frac {4}{n ^ {2} \\pi^ {2}} [ (- 1) ^ {n} - 1 ] = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l l} - \\frac {8}{n ^ {2} \\pi^ {2}}, & n = 1, 3, 5, \\dots , \\\\ 0, & n = 2, 4, 6, \\dots , \\end{array} \\right. \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
