        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.872,
                0.774,
                0.902
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "六、【解】由 \\(\\int_{L}2xy\\mathrm{d}x + Q(x,y)\\mathrm{d}y\\) 与路径无关得 \\(\\frac{\\partial Q}{\\partial x} = 2x\\) ，则 \\(Q(x,y) = x^{2} + \\varphi (y)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.907,
                0.68,
                0.937
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\int_ {(0, 0)} ^ {(t, 1)} 2 x y \\mathrm {d} x + Q (x, y) \\mathrm {d} y = \\int_ {0} ^ {t} 0 \\mathrm {d} x + \\int_ {0} ^ {1} [ t ^ {2} + \\varphi (y) ] \\mathrm {d} y = t ^ {2} + \\int_ {0} ^ {1} \\varphi (y) \\mathrm {d} y,\n\\]"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.069,
                0.66,
                0.098
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\int_ {(0, 0)} ^ {(1, t)} 2 x y \\mathrm {d} x + Q (x, y) \\mathrm {d} y = \\int_ {0} ^ {1} 0 \\mathrm {d} x + \\int_ {0} ^ {t} [ 1 + \\varphi (y) ] \\mathrm {d} y = t + \\int_ {0} ^ {t} \\varphi (y) \\mathrm {d} y,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.104,
                0.51,
                0.132
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(t + \\int_0^t\\varphi (y)\\mathrm{d}y = t^2 +\\int_0^1\\varphi (y)\\mathrm{d}y\\) 得 \\(\\varphi (t) = 2t - 1\\)"
