        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.182,
                0.661,
                0.197
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由罗尔定理，存在 \\(\\xi_1\\in (a,c),\\xi_2\\in (c,b)\\) ，使得 \\(g^{\\prime}(\\xi_{1}) = g^{\\prime}(\\xi_{2}) = 0\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.203,
                0.729,
                0.218
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "再由罗尔定理，存在 \\(\\xi \\in (a,b)\\) ，使得 \\(g^{\\prime \\prime}(\\xi) = 0\\) ，矛盾，故在 \\((a,b)\\) 内 \\(g(x)\\neq 0\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.224,
                0.436,
                0.24
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2) 令 \\(\\varphi(x) = f(x)g'(x) - f'(x)g(x)\\),"
