                0.08,
                0.245,
                0.661,
                0.261
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(\\varphi(a) = \\varphi(b) = 0\\)，由罗尔定理知，存在 \\(\\xi \\in (a, b)\\)，使 \\(\\varphi'(\\xi) = 0\\)，即"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.38,
                0.265,
                0.629,
                0.283
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nf (\\xi) g ^ {\\prime \\prime} (\\xi) - f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (\\xi) g (\\xi) = 0,\n\\]"
