            "content": "八、【解】设 \\(\\pmb {\\xi} = (x_{1},x_{2},x_{3})^{\\mathrm{T}}\\) 为 \\(\\lambda_{2} = \\lambda_{3} = 1\\) 对应的特征向量，"
        },
        {
