            "content": "由 \\(\\xi_1^{\\mathrm{T}}\\xi = 0\\) 得 \\(x_{2} + x_{3} = 0\\) ，则 \\(\\lambda_{2} = \\lambda_{3} = 1\\) 对应的线性无关的特征向量为"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.392,
                0.39,
                0.617,
                0.446
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\pmb {\\xi} _ {2} = \\left( \\begin{array}{c} 1 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 0 \\end{array} \\right), \\quad \\pmb {\\xi} _ {3} = \\left( \\begin{array}{c} 0 \\\\ 1 \\\\ - 1 \\end{array} \\right),\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.453,
                0.507,
                0.509
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "令 \\(\\pmb{P} = \\left( \\begin{array}{rrr}0 & 1 & 0\\\\ 1 & 0 & 1\\\\ 1 & 0 & -1 \\end{array} \\right)\\) ，由 \\(\\pmb{P}^{-1}\\pmb {A}\\pmb {P} = \\left( \\begin{array}{rrr} - 1 & 0 & 0\\\\ 0 & 1 & 0\\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{array} \\right)\\) 得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.324,
                0.516,
                0.682,
                0.572
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\mathbf {A} = \\mathbf {P} \\left( \\begin{array}{c c c} - 1 & 0 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 1 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{array} \\right) \\mathbf {P} ^ {- 1} = \\left( \\begin{array}{c c c} 1 & 0 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 0 & - 1 \\\\ 0 & - 1 & 0 \\end{array} \\right).\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.053,
                0.578,
                0.614,
                0.595
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "九、【解】方法一 由 \\(\\mathbf{A}\\mathbf{A}^{\\mathrm{T}} = \\mathbf{E}\\) 得 \\(|\\mathbf{A}|\\cdot |\\mathbf{A}^{\\mathrm{T}}| = 1\\) ，即 \\(|\\mathbf{A}|^2 = 1\\)"
        },
