        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.08,
                0.621,
                0.758,
                0.637
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "于是 \\(|\\mathbf{A} + \\mathbf{E}| = |\\mathbf{A} + \\mathbf{A}\\mathbf{A}^{\\mathrm{T}}| = |\\mathbf{A}|\\cdot |\\mathbf{E} + \\mathbf{A}^{\\mathrm{T}}| = -|\\left(\\mathbf{E} + \\mathbf{A}\\right)^{\\mathrm{T}}| = -|\\mathbf{E} + \\mathbf{A}|\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.643,
                0.218,
                0.658
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(|\\mathbf{E} + \\mathbf{A}| = 0\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.665,
                0.35,
                0.679
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "方法二 令 \\(AX = \\lambda X(X\\neq 0)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.685,
                0.464,
                0.7
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(\\mathbf{A}\\mathbf{X} = \\lambda \\mathbf{X}\\) 得 \\(\\mathbf{X}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\mathbf{A}^{\\mathrm{T}} = \\lambda \\mathbf{X}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\) ，两边右乘 \\(\\mathbf{A}\\mathbf{X}\\) 得"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.705,
                0.629,
                0.72
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(\\mathbf{X}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\mathbf{A}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\cdot \\mathbf{A}\\mathbf{X} = \\lambda \\mathbf{X}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\cdot \\mathbf{A}\\mathbf{X}\\) ，即 \\(\\pmb {X}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\pmb {X} = \\lambda^{2}\\pmb{X}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\pmb {X}\\) ，或 \\((\\lambda^2 -1)\\pmb{X}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\pmb {X} = \\mathbf{0}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.726,
                0.499,
                0.741
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(\\mathbf{X}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\mathbf{X} = \\| \\mathbf{X}\\|^2 >0\\) 得 \\(\\lambda^2 -1 = 0\\) ，即 \\(\\lambda = \\pm 1\\)"
        },
