            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.853,
                0.677,
                0.868
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(E(X) = np = 4\\) ， \\(D(X) = np(1 - p) = 10 \\times 0.4 \\times 0.6 = 2.4\\) ，得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.306,
                0.873,
                0.71,
                0.889
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nE \\left(X ^ {2}\\right) = D (X) + \\left[ E (X) \\right] ^ {2} = 2. 4 + 1 6 = 1 8. 4.\n\\]"
