        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.107,
                0.759,
                0.134
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】令 \\(A = \\{X\\geqslant 0\\} ,B = \\{Y\\geqslant 0\\}\\) ，则 \\(P(A) = P(B) = \\frac{4}{7},P(AB) = \\frac{3}{7},\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.142,
                0.733,
                0.156
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "于是 \\(P\\{\\max (X,Y)\\geqslant 0\\} = 1 - P\\{\\max (X,Y) <   0\\} = 1 - P\\{X <   0,Y <   0\\}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.142,
                0.733,
                0.212
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} = 1 - P (\\bar {A} \\cdot \\bar {B}) = 1 - P (\\bar {A + B}) = P (A + B) \\\\ = P (A) + P (B) - P (A B) = \\frac {5}{7}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
