            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(y \\geqslant 1\\) 时，\\(F_{Y}(y) = P\\{X \\leqslant \\ln y\\} = \\int_{0}^{\\ln y} \\mathrm{e}^{-x} \\, \\mathrm{d}x = -\\mathrm{e}^{-x}\\left| \\begin{array}{c} \\ln y \\\\ 0 \\end{array} \\right| = 1 - \\frac{1}{y}\\)，"
