            "content": "即 \\(F_{Y}(y) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}0, & y < 1,\\\\ 1 - \\frac{1}{y}, & y\\geqslant 1, \\end{array} \\right.\\) 故 \\(Y = \\mathrm{e}^{X}\\) 的概率密度为"
