            "content": "\\[\nf _ {Y} (y) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l l} 0, & y <   1, \\\\ \\frac {1}{y ^ {2}}, & y \\geqslant 1. \\end{array} \\right.\n\\]"
        }
